(475, 1, '2016-07-26 01:34:47', '2016-07-26 01:34:47', '<img src="http://localhost/daily/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/amasipsip-300x210.png" width="300" height="210" srcset="http://localhost/daily/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/amasipsip-300x210.png 300w, http://localhost/daily/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/amasipsip-768x539.png 768w, http://localhost/daily/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/amasipsip-480x337.png 480w, http://localhost/daily/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/amasipsip-230x161.png 230w, http://localhost/daily/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/amasipsip-350x245.png 350w, http://localhost/daily/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/amasipsip.png 800w" class="so-widget-image">\r\n<h3 class="widget-title">Ama SipSip Milk Maheu</h3>			A tantalising blend of the creamiest milk and the freshest fruits is used to create the ultimate energy food drink experience. This blend of milk and strawberries, buttermilk or vanilla custard merge to create an exciting mix for your drinking pleasure. With so much variety, there is plenty to experience and explore. Choose from any of the enticing flavours that make the perfect meal on-the-go.\r\n<h3>Available in 4 flavours:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Vanilla Custard</li>\r\n<li>Buttermilk</li>\r\n<li>Strawberry Milk</li>\r\n<li>Choc Milk</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img src="http://localhost/daily/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/milk_maheu_butter_milk200px-130x300.png" width="130" height="300" srcset="http://localhost/daily/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/milk_maheu_butter_milk200px-130x300.png 130w, http://localhost/daily/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/milk_maheu_butter_milk200px.png 200w" class="so-widget-image">\r\n<h3 class="widget-title">Ama SipSip Plain Maheu Maize Drinks</h3>			A unique, traditional energy drink from a blend of the freshest fruit and cereal. Best served cold, Ama SipSip makes for a delicious refreshment and healthy drink combined with a texture and smoothness that only Ama SipSip can give. Our traditional maheu is presented in a variety of distinct flavours. Its distinctive flavour and smoothness has made it a favourite satisfying healthy drink..\r\n<h3>Available in 4 flavours:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Traditional</li>\r\n<li>Butter Cream</li>\r\n<li>Banana</li>\r\n<li>Strawberry</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img src="http://localhost/daily/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/maheu_butter_cream200px-130x300.png" width="130" height="300" srcset="http://localhost/daily/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/maheu_butter_cream200px-130x300.png 130w, http://localhost/daily/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/maheu_butter_cream200px.png 200w" class="so-widget-image">\r\n<h2>Get your unique, traditional energy drink and experience the smoothness only Ama SipSip can give!<br>\r\n<a class="readmore" href="#">Buy Now</a></h2>', 'AMA SipSip', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ama-sipsip', '', '', '2016-07-27 02:41:26', '2016-07-27 02:41:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/daily/?page_id=475', 0, 'page', '', 0),
