(486, 1, '2016-07-26 01:38:44', '2016-07-26 01:38:44', '<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_0">\r\n<h1>About Dairy Gold</h1>\r\nDairy Gold is a manufacturer of dairy and processed traditional drinks in Zambia, focusing on the central and southern African region. Dairy Gold is part of the Trade Kings Group, which is one of the largest independent FMCG manufacturers in central Africa.\r\n\r\nOur adopted a people-focused approach ensures that we are committed to creating world-class drink manufacturing facilities, products and brands. We believe in investing and developing the local economy and have, therefore, localised job creation for Zambian natives.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_1">\r\n<h2>The Dairy Gold Promise</h2>\r\nThe Dairy Gold standard of quality ensures that we produce only the best tasting, healthiest, remarkable beverage choices.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_2">\r\n<h2>The Dairy Gold Aim</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>To emerge from the current position of a localised dairy and traditional leader as a leading beverage brand in the region.</li>\r\n 	<li>To continue manufacturing the highest standard, most innovative, tastiest and affordable drinks that offer not only satisfaction to consumers, but ensure a healthy, consistent and high-quality food-drink alternative.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe invite you to explore our range of products. If you have any enquiries, feedback, or if you would like to find out about distributorship, you can e-mail us at <a href="mailto:info@dairygold.co.zm">info@dairygold.co.zm</a> or call +260 211 849040.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '467-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-26 01:38:44', '2016-07-26 01:38:44', '', 467, 'http://localhost/daily/2016/07/26/467-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
