(488, 1, '2016-07-26 01:40:14', '2016-07-26 01:40:14', '<h1>Contact Us</h1>\r\nAt Dairy Gold we provide traditional wholesome on-the-go drinking meals packed with nutrients for the entire family!\r\n<h4>The tastier and healthier beverage of choice.</h4>\r\n<strong>Physical Address:</strong>\r\nPlot No. 80888\r\nOff Mumbwa Road\r\nLusaka\r\nZambia\r\n\r\n<strong>Business Hours:</strong>\r\n08:00 – 17:00\r\n\r\n<strong>Telephone:</strong>\r\n+260 211 849040\r\n\r\n<strong>Email:</strong>\r\n<a href="mailto:info@dairygold.co.zm">info@dairygold.co.zm</a>', 'Contact', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '473-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-26 01:40:14', '2016-07-26 01:40:14', '', 473, 'http://localhost/daily/2016/07/26/473-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(489, 1, '2016-07-26 01:41:22', '2016-07-26 01:41:22', '<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_0">\r\n<h1>Ama SipSip Milk Maheu</h1>\r\nA tantalising blend of the creamiest milk and the freshest fruits is used to create the ultimate energy food drink experience. This blend of milk and strawberries, buttermilk or vanilla custard merge to create an exciting mix for your drinking pleasure. With so much variety, there is plenty to experience and explore. Choose from any of the enticing flavours that make the perfect meal on-the-go.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_1">\r\n<h2>Available in 4 flavours:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Vanilla Custard</li>\r\n 	<li>Buttermilk</li>\r\n 	<li>Strawberry Milk</li>\r\n 	<li>Choc Milk</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_2">\r\n<h1>Ama SipSip Plain Maheu Maize Drinks</h1>\r\nA unique, traditional energy drink from a blend of the freshest fruit and cereal. Best served cold, Ama SipSip makes for a delicious refreshment and healthy drink combined with a texture and smoothness that only Ama SipSip can give. Our traditional maheu is presented in a variety of distinct flavours. Its distinctive flavour and smoothness has made it a favourite satisfying healthy drink..\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_3">\r\n<h2>Available in 4 flavours:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Traditional</li>\r\n 	<li>Butter Cream</li>\r\n 	<li>Banana</li>\r\n 	<li>Strawberry</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'AMA SipSip', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '475-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-26 01:41:22', '2016-07-26 01:41:22', '', 475, 'http://localhost/daily/2016/07/26/475-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(490, 1, '2016-07-26 01:42:06', '2016-07-26 01:42:06', '<div class=" et_pb_row et_pb_row_0">\r\n<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4  et_pb_column_0">\r\n<div class="et_pb_module et-waypoint et_pb_image et_pb_animation_off et_pb_image_0 et_always_center_on_mobile et-animated"><img src="http://dairygoldcozm.my-new-website.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/sip_it_up_payline.png" alt="" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=" et_pb_row et_pb_row_1">\r\n<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_2_3  et_pb_column_1">\r\n<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_0">\r\n<h1>Shake ‘n Sip</h1>\r\nFor sustained energy and ultra-nutrition, Shake ‘n Sip Fruity Milk offers consumers the best of both worlds. It is the all-in-one choice for a refreshing, fast-acting energy blend. A wholesome combination of our creamy yoghurt blended with a selection of with banana, pineapples or mixed berries create a fruity blend that promotes an active lifestyle. Shake ‘n Sip is a delicious and convenient way to get your daily boost and nutrition.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_1">\r\n<h2>Available in 4 flavours:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Traditional</li>\r\n 	<li>Butter Cream</li>\r\n 	<li>Banana</li>\r\n 	<li>Strawberry</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Shake'' Sip', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '478-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-26 01:42:06', '2016-07-26 01:42:06', '', 478, 'http://localhost/daily/2016/07/26/478-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
